FruityShell v1.0
------------------
Allows you to control FruityWiFi using a metasploit-ish type of shell.
FruityWiFi needs to be up an running.


MENU
--------
?                Help menu
exit             Exit the console
clear            Clear the console
show modules     Show modules list
set              Sets module status //set module/{name} start|stop
use              Uses config|module //use module/{name}


MENU-MODULE
-----------
?                Help menu
back             Move back from current context
clear            Clear the console
exit             Exit the console
start            Starts current module
stop             Stops current module
status           Show current module status
show options     Show module options [to be implemented...]


MENU-CONFIG
-----------
?                Help menu
back             Move back from current context
clear            Clear the console
exit             Exit the console
show options     Show config options
set              Set config options //set {property} {value}


CONFIG (init.conf)
------
[api] Setup API details (server and token) to access FruityWiFi.


DEPENDENCIES
------------
apt-get -y install python-requests
apt-get -y install python-configobj

apt-get -p install python-pip
pip install --upgrade requests
